title: Kono Yakuza, Intelli-butta Kedamono.: Mata wo Hiraite Ore wo Sasoe
original_name: このヤクザ、インテリぶったケダモノ。～股を開いて俺を誘え
sinopse:
"Do you really think you can entice men with such clumsy kisses?" He may be rough, but there's nothing she can do against the Yakuza's insistent caresses...

(Source: WWWave Corporation)
